strings: <voice_0x01001C5C><se_high>Media princess: Thank you for the quote <hero>
<voice_0x01001C5D><se_high>Media princess: This is your only opportunity to forget your worries and relax.
<voice_0x01001C5E><se_high>Media princess: I miss the time we spent together in the palace...
<voice_0x01001C60><se_high>Media princess: We were young and every time I wake up I remember my childhood.
<voice_0x01001C61><se_high>Media princess: Always on the run <hero> I'll do my best to catch up!
<voice_0x01001C62><se_high>Media princess: Yes, you can feel that spring has arrived. Hopefully we can talk soon <hero> I miss you so much!
